rows.label: tlk45710153_03_msg0001
rows.name:
So I hear Chairman Bahn
has gone missing.

rows.label: tlk45710153_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I'd rather not return to the Guild right
now for fear of getting mixed up in that
mess. I think I might just stay here.

rows.label: tlk45710153_03_msg0003
rows.name:
By the way, have you ever noticed
the strange inscriptions on the
backs of the walls around here?

rows.label: tlk45710153_03_msg0004
rows.name:
They've bothered me since I was a
boy, but now I have some free time,
I might actually look into them.

rows.label: tlk45710153_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Freedom is a wonderful thing, you
know? Without work to tie me down,
it feels like the world is my oyster!

rows.label: tlk45710153_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Though the lack of income
could be a small problem.
